---
const techStack = [
	"Python",
	".NET Core",
	"Java",
	"Machine Learning",
	"AI/LLMs",
	"Data Analysis"
];
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 px-6">
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
		<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">
			About Me
		</h2>

		<div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
			<p>
				I'm a <strong class="text-white">Generative AI Specialist</strong> and <strong class="text-white">Data Scientist</strong> with extensive experience building intelligent solutions that solve real-world problems.
			</p>

			<p>
				With many years as a software developer, I bring a strong technical foundation in <strong class="text-white">.NET Core, Java, and Python</strong>. This diverse background allows me to bridge the gap between cutting-edge AI research and practical, production-ready applications.
			</p>

			<p>
				I'm passionate about leveraging data and AI to create meaningful impact, whether that's through building ML models, developing generative AI applications, or architecting scalable software systems.
			</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Tech Stack Pills -->
		<div class="mt-10">
			<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-center text-gray-400">Technologies & Tools</h3>
			<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
				{techStack.map(tech => (
					<span class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-800 text-emerald-400 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-gray-700">
						{tech}
					</span>
				))}
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
